				<p uri="/liahona/2006/05/36.p2" class="" id="p2">Susan W. Tanner</p>
				<p uri="/liahona/2006/05/36.p3" class="" id="p3">Presidenta General de las Mujeres J&oacute;venes</p>
			</div>
